Sequence diagram: 

Julia goes to website to see available properties
	website loads
		- loads react frontend
			-request data from backend via webservice
				-webservice returns the information from local storage/json files
		-callback function will generate card data
		-website will return data to julia

Julia will click on the 2 bedroom card to filter the apartments she wants to see
	website will load the rental properties page
	- loads react frontend
		-request data from backend via webservice
			-webservice requests data from database
			-webservice will load data from database
			-webservice will return the information on 2 bedroom apartments
	-callback function will generate card data
	-website will return data to julia

Julia will select the dates she wants to stay 
	website will load the rental properties page
	- loads react frontend
		-request data from backend via webservice
			-webservice requests data from database
			-webservice will load data from database
			-webservice will return the information on 2 bedroom apartments during the dates chosen
	-callback function will generate card data
	-website will return data to julia

Julia will select the apartment card of the apartment she wants to stay in
	website will load apartment page
	- loads react frontend
		-request data from backend via webservice
			-webservice requests data from database
			-webservice will load data from database
			-webservice will return the information the aparment chosen
	-callback function will generate card data
	-website will return data to julia

Julia selects the book apartment button
	website will load the login page/moadal
	- loads react frontend
	- loads the form information from the backend
	-website will return data to julia

Julia will fill out the form and login in
	loads react frontend
		-send data from backend via webservice
			-data will be sent to database to create her account
			-data will be sent to the database to create her booking
	-callback function will generate card data
	-website will return data to julia with the modal to confirm her booking

Julia navigates back to the home page by clicking the home button on nav bar
	website loads
		- loads react frontend
			-request data from backend via webservice
				-webservice returns the information from local storage/json files
		-website will return data to julia

Julia wants to look at the things to do in the area so clicks on the things to do card:
	website will load apartment page
	- loads react frontend
		-request data from backend via webservice
			-webservice requests data from database
			-webservice will load data from database
			-webservice will return the information from things to do
	-callback function will generate card data
	-website will return data to julia

Julia is interested in dining so clicks on the dining filter
	website will load apartment page
	- loads react frontend
		-request data from backend via webservice
			-webservice requests data from database
			-webservice will load data from database
			-webservice will return the information from things to do filtering for dining
	-callback function will generate card data
	-website will return data to julia	



